{"tid":849344,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch]Mario Party屌你老母中哂伏","createTime":"2018-10-05T15:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T10:49:26.000Z","uid":71463,"like":46,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9b0560e30f4c7a35cec721a5373a3c7ce4359e94","tid":849344,"uid":71463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"知道10月5號Mario Party有得買，滿心歡喜同朋友收工沖去買啦<br />\n返到屋企開GAME諗住連線3個人玩，當初都知道要買Switch Online嘅，<br />\nok唔緊要，我只要同朋友連到機，3條友玩大富翁就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但入到Game原來唔可以連機玩?</span>得個Online Mode可以邀朋友一齊入房玩，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但呢個Mode竟然得5隻Mini Game?</span></span><br />\n我屌你老母咩，姐係話如果我想同朋友3個人玩大富翁玩齊80隻Mini Game，<br />\n就一定要見面玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家咩年代呀大佬，中撚哂大伏呀救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係我唔識連線炸，有無教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9dc97eb02ab0b73949b6b3981475f756bdf476","tid":849344,"uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6aa12cfcce606734cf52db58c923c047dec2d0","tid":849344,"uid":71463,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ec9dc97eb02ab0b73949b6b3981475f756bdf476","tid":849344,"uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,